pullrequest.title: Model submission for Husky sensor configuration 1 from team CoSTAR

content.raw:
Looks good to me! I noticed the RGBD depth image “DepthCloud” \(in white\) has a rotated transform but that seems to be consistent with other vehicles.

\(robotName was “X2” but I was testing the CoSTAR Husky model\)
